cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CV 

This paper presents a novel neural network architecture, specifically designed for processing multi-dimensional data as a single entity. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including neural networks (cs.NE), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), signal processing (cs.SI), and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the computational experiments conducted to evaluate the performance of the proposed architecture, which further supports the possibility of it belonging to these sub-categories.
